EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO TOWNS AND CITIES -- LOW AND MODERATE INCOME HOUSING
***
1 This act would ensure that the Rhode Island department of housing is able to access the
2 full calendar year worth of housing choice voucher data for the annual report required by this
3 section by moving the report submission deadline back to align with availability of federal data and
4 would amend the content of the information required to be submitted in the annual report.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
